article.story: CLEVELAND -- — Jayson Woodrich scored 14 points and grabbed eight rebounds and Cleveland State beat Division III-level Penn State-Behrend 89-47 on Saturday. Yahel Hill had 13 points for Cleveland State (4-2) which won its fourth straight. Deante Johnson and D'Moi Hodge each scored 11 points.
